{"tid":2451041,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"奧巴馬回應亞特蘭大槍擊案　稱反亞裔暴力事件令人震驚  警方指疑兇聲稱非針對亞裔","createTime":"2021-03-17T23:24:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T07:00:58.000Z","uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"921c0bd9e7383a0a84b1a4b851c9803468e09532","tid":2451041,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:24:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">奧巴馬回應亞特蘭大槍擊案　稱反亞裔暴力事件令人震驚<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581167-20210317.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581167-20210317.htm&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2csFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=80530a0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581167-20210317.htm&h=c8783e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581167-20210317.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國前總統奧巴馬，對佐治亞州亞特蘭大造成8人死亡的槍擊案，表示哀悼。案中至少6人為亞裔女性。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬慰問所有死者家屬，他表示，慘劇再度顯示槍械管制方面仍有很多工作要做，另外，雖然兇徒的行兇動機未明，但從遇害者的身份，顯示反亞裔的暴力事件令人震驚，認為這些行為必須結束。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">美國佐治亞州釀8死槍擊案　警方指疑兇聲稱非針對亞裔</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581192-20210318.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581192-20210318.htm&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2csFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=e088b602\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581192-20210318.htm&h=13896469\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581192-20210318.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國佐治亞州亞特蘭大造成8人死亡槍擊案，警方表示，疑犯承認犯案，透露有性上癮問題，並非針對亞裔。<br />\n<br />\n當地兩間水療中心及一間按摩院先後發生槍擊，部分人當場中槍死亡。8名死者中至少6名是亞裔女性，其中4人是韓裔，警方表示，疑犯似乎經常前往出事的美容按摩店，被捕時正要去佛羅里達，可能計劃另一宗槍擊。<br />\n<br />\n這宗是美國今年第六宗大型兇殺案，亦是自2019年8月俄亥俄州兇殺案後，死亡人數最多的兇殺。白宮表示，總統拜登已經聽取匯報，副總統賀錦麗亦表達向亞裔美國人社區的支持。"},{"pid":"957afd07aded677a479f53201eb3cfb617467816","tid":2451041,"uid":154486,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:27:19.000Z","msg":"而家個美國總統叫奧巴馬咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38546af5b15292503fffe857041fee59996bad4f","tid":2451041,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:28:07.000Z","msg":"黑左奧巴馬，執政8年養到中共肥肥白白<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/1024/branded_zhongwen/5074/production/_96969502_78b75efc-37fe-449f-944e-0fa30805a597.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_zhongwen%2F5074%2Fproduction%2F_96969502_78b75efc-37fe-449f-944e-0fa30805a597.jpg&h=e3a993a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff233b7d917879a0955525e8c65cce56f0d61bae","tid":2451041,"uid":75487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:29:00.000Z","msg":"BOT定真人啊<br />\n唔想答啦"},{"pid":"8554db621a875877c19a8d6abbc946f4a88d6144","tid":2451041,"uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:29:35.000Z","msg":"因為兇手係白人就識得感到震驚<br />\n如果係burn loot murder就忽然隱形<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd7476bcb0688c018e333726154169f49fea72c","tid":2451041,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T23:29:46.000Z","msg":"White House Press Sec. says there is &quot;no question&quot; that the Trump administration calling COVID the 'Wuhan virus' has led to uptick in attacks on Asian Americans<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dailycaller/status/1372288099389165572?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdailycaller%2Fstatus%2F1372288099389165572%3Fs%3D21&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2csFuFiCHHua96MUfZSGoRU%3D&h=7edc2ac4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdailycaller%2Fstatus%2F1372288099389165572%3Fs%3D21&h=9